ing model with good precision\nand tested other predictions of non-unitary conformal field theory. This work\npaves the way for the first experimental observation of the central charge of\nnon-unitary conformal field theory.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Aug 2017 07:31:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 26 Feb 2018 10:05:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-02-27"}
